DOC.brief_summary: To compare the efficacy of transcervical double balloon catheters versus controlled release dinoprostone vaginal inserts for pre-induction cervical ripening in term women with unfavourable cervices.
DOC.brief_title: Double Balloon Catheter Versus Dinoprostone Vaginal Insert for Cervical Ripening.
